msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/linalg/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.linalg.solve:46
msgid ""
"`a` must be square and of full-rank, i.e., all rows (or, equivalently, "
"columns) must be linearly independent; if either is not true, use `lstsq` "
"for the least-squares best \"solution\" of the system/equation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/linalg/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.linalg.solve:53
msgid ""
"The b array is only treated as a shape (M,) column vector if it is exactly 1-"
"dimensional. In all other instances it is treated as a stack of (M, K) "
"matrices. Previously b would be treated as a stack of (M,) vectors if b.ndim "
"was equal to a.ndim - 1."
msgstr ""

